{"tid":979470,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I][Gen4][Raid] Pokemon Go (26) 交友請先睇#1","createTime":"2019-01-12T16:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T10:17:57.000Z","uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5cc3d2681178dd4d32aef093b0af712630f74d","tid":979470,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"交友可以入黎哩到填表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/8cV5Dx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8cV5Dx&d=b%2BxmfEbLSqO0816Tk%2Fy04ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=73c47b2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/8cV5Dx</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：我想問呢，皮卡丘伊布胡地肯泰羅臭臭花卡蒂狗凱羅斯快龍拉普拉斯臭泥超夢...<br />\nA：冇人識你呢堆咩嚟，想討論唔該用返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港式譯名</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://n1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn1.hkgpkm.pw&d=b%2BxmfEbLSqO0816Tk%2Fy04ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3290bc69\" target=\"_blank\">http://n1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://n2.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hkgpkm.pw&d=b%2BxmfEbLSqO0816Tk%2Fy04ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8944b27a\" target=\"_blank\">http://n2.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：有無地圖可以用？<br />\nA：Wecatch，但唔係全港都用到，有時會出問題。依家多左個新功能 - 可以睇任務（都係局部性地區限定）<br />\n<br />\nQ：仲有無巢？<br />\nA：有，兩個星期轉一次。Telegram add howishkpoorguy<br />\n<br />\nQ：用咩可以check IV？<br />\nA：Calcy IV / Poke Genie<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解啲CP同以前好似唔同左？<br />\nA：N記早排調整左<br />\n<br />\nQ：GPS Not Found (11)點搞？<br />\nA：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fCdkgEX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fCdkgEX</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：幾時出翻超夢夢 / 三神鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA：請Email俾N記<br />\n<br />\nQ：XXX 100 IV係幾多CP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA：Google快過你係到等答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ：去邊到入Telegram Group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA：@HKPGC<br />\n<br />\nQ : 我有兩隻XXX, 一隻 YY IV有ZZ攻, 另一隻BB IV但AA攻, 升邊隻好？<br />\nA : 自己見到邊隻順眼就升邊隻, 同一隻升爆嘅小精靈0 IV比100 IV只係差少少, 真係咁執着嘅話邊隻15/最高攻就升邊隻<br />\n<br />\nQ：一入Game就彈，點搞？<br />\nA：An機嘅話試下呢度幾步，每一步唔得就去下一步：<br />\n1. 清快取(Cache)<br />\n2. 清資料 (之後要再Login過)<br />\n3. 剷App再裝過<br />\n<br />\niOS：有用Apple Watch的話，Hide咗Watch入面嘅Pok&eacute;mon Go先，再試下喺電話重入Game<br />\n<br />\nQ：點樣永續龍任？<br />\nA：常設龍任係捉龍送迷你龍<br />\n轉到龍任嘅話就用之前搞掂嘅迷你龍嚟完任，再「逃走」將啱啱搞掂嘅龍任迷你龍擱置等下個龍任先捉<br />\n<br />\nQ：啲精靈係Random定好似以前咁有巢？<br />\nA：平時有巢，兩個禮拜轉一次（巢穴資料請add howishkpoorguy）<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩係亮晶晶？<br />\nA：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fOfNOrX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fOfNOrX</a>"},{"pid":"978eae0d5c9ec5ce92f9b361b4d9e1c78e54877c","tid":979470,"uid":3290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此Post嚴禁外掛飛狗或無限分身參與討論</span><br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">一番槍</span>&quot; (ID: 24121) / &quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">9upperrrrrrr</span>&quot; (ID: 161126) 為<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>爛口外掛賤種飛狗</strong></span><br />\n請大家遠離，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿回覆/引用</span>以上賤種飛狗一切回應</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其他外掛賤種</span>：<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">人生失敗</span>&quot; (ID: 592)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">搶奬家姐研</span>&quot; (ID: 78546)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">歐陽儉</span>&quot; (ID: 66618)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">海馬囝</span>&quot; (ID: 28623)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">八支八支半</span>&quot; (ID: 27432)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">滑蛋豬扒飯</span>&quot; (ID: 31521)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">食得哂先至好嗌</span>&quot; (ID: 146063)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">辣椒真係好好食</span>&quot; (ID: 157862)<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">紅魔